\headerbox{Sample collection}{name=meth,column=2,row=0}{
\textbf{Location:} Heron Island, ciguateric web of Great Barrier Reef, Australia (23$^{\circ}$ 4420' S, 151$^{\circ}$ 9140' E).\\
\textbf{Macroalgal samples:} \emph{Halimeda} sp. in October 2013, \emph{Padina} sp. in July 2014.\\
\textbf{Cultures:}  Five clonal strains of  established (HG1, HG4, HG6, HG7 and HG26) and maintained in F/10 medium \cite{holmes}. 
at 27$^{\circ}$C, 60 mol/m/s light in 12h:12h light to dark cycles.
}


